    <p type="title">OAHPA! Vocabulary</p>
    <p>In the OAHPA! vocabulary we have also collected the words from the following textbooks:</p>
    <list>
      <p type="listitem" xml:lang="sme">Davvin 1-4</p>
      <p type="listitem" xml:lang="sme">Sárá ja su ustibat</p>
      <p type="listitem">Bures, bures fas</p>
